   <head>[Epitaph on Mrs Mason]</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Tell them, though 'tis an awful thing to die</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">('Twas ev'n to thee) yet the dread path once trod,</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Heaven lifts its everlasting portals high</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">And bids ''the pure in heart behold their God.''</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
